I make build.xml file and deploy my application to tomcat 5.0.28 server.
Deploy is successfully finished, but ant says "BUILD FAILED". The reason why ant
says BUILD FAILED is AbstractCatalinaTask.java line 222.

if (!line.startsWith("OK -")) {
    error = line;
}

This code is corrent if we use English locale. But other locale, Manager Servlet
response is not "OK -". Therefore ant says "BUILD FAILED" even though deploy or
undeploy is successfully finished.
